{"tid":1387279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢夢到漆彈大作戰","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T13:50:46.000Z","uid":294710,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"363fe99fb60d7721c298decead6ecba79e5b4345","tid":1387279,"uid":294710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:32:30.000Z","msg":"對方變成重裝甲動物小隊，絕招係短距離衝刺，令玩家離場<br />\n但重裝甲嘅弱點係視線，只要視線受阻就會失去戰鬥力<br />\n而玩家新增副武器，手搖噴漆<br />\n可以係對方衝刺時噴對方眼罩，達到短暫失明嘅效果 <br />\n如果對方除眼罩可以補多一嘢，之後可以選擇進攻/逃跑/救人 <br />\n通常對方十幾個人一齊衝，要扮跑再回馬槍噴，要確保所有人中招<br />\n還新增一個小動作，一齊搖只要夠齊夠多人，可以震懾對方 <br />\n手搖噴漆在商店購買，三十個硬幣，每人必備一罐防動物<br />\n<br />\n我夢到係Splatoon，未玩過，有無巴打知係咪咁玩？定係我夢到下個Expansion？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/LzMCN68CGL4/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FLzMCN68CGL4%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=4d6cd06d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c40238174bde0b5ac2ef80ac67c31249a74d5377","tid":1387279,"uid":153245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"如果有人派槍派子彈嘅話 有得玩啊"},{"pid":"ef1fc7386f9d0b675b2f430497c848f37674c486","tid":1387279,"uid":153245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"反正年輕人機動性同靈活性咁強"},{"pid":"48bfc0295b51a416d03c0b5d77915743abb40f62","tid":1387279,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:40:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387135\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387135</a>"},{"pid":"56e3277e56da7a1fa9d1ce4c726d50400ed51f46","tid":1387279,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"［神器開箱］八月就到，又係Ocamp水戰嘅時候<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387135</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9b2df2cd61a54daf342be0bea72a1cfd30adbe3","tid":1387279,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c40238174bde0b5ac2ef80ac67c31249a74d5377","tid